<style>
    :root {
        --primary: #bda581;
        --bg-card: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    
    .dev-container { 
        max-width: 800px; 
        margin: 80px auto; 
        padding: 50px; 
        background: var(--bg-card); 
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); 
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.1);
        border-radius: 16px; 
        text-align: center; 
        box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out forwards; 
    }
    .dev-icon { font-size: 4rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 25px; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.2)); }
    .dev-container h1 { color: #fff; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .dev-container p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 35px; line-height: 1.6; }
    
    .dev-stats { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #cbd5e1; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    
    .progress-bar-container { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px; margin-bottom: 40px; overflow: hidden; }
    .progress-bar { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8a7657 0%, var(--primary) 100%); height: 10px; border-radius: 10px; width: 35%; transition: width 1s ease-in-out; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.5); }
    
    .btn-back { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background: rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.1); border: 1px solid var(--primary); color: var(--primary); padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: all 0.3s; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .btn-back:hover { background: var(--primary); color: #07090e; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.4); transform: translateY(-2px); }
</style>

<div class="dev-container">
    <div class="dev-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
    </div>
    <h1>Module Formations</h1>
    <p>Cette section permettra de gérer le suivi, les brevets et les qualifications des agents du BCSO. Elle est actuellement en cours de développement par le Haut Commandement.</p>
    
    <div class="dev-stats">
        Développement de la base de données : 35%
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar-container">
        <div class="progress-bar"></div>
    </div>

    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-back"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Retour au tableau de bord</a>
</div>